Newsmax.com, one of America's leading online news services, is conducting an urgent national online poll about President Obama's healthcare plan, the Supreme Court ruling and whether the plan should be repealed.
Newsmax will provide the results of this poll to major media outlets.
Newsmax's results also will be shared with popular radio talk-show hosts across America.
Newsmax reports have been cited by major media outlets, including CNN, ABC News, Fox News, CBS, MSNBC, and other major networks.
Hundreds of media outlets have reported on Newsmax's online polls.